{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/intro_gif.gif?t=1739957635\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/Add_a_heading_sample.png?t=1739957635\" /><strong>Metaball is a free-to-play, crossplay-enabled online multiplayer sports game that combines fast-paced movements, thrilling PvP matches, and advanced team play.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You play as a Rider, trying to bring fame and wealth to his name by winning merciless Metaball League games with his teammates and collecting Metanium and MVP points.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/Unleash_your_creativity_600x104_.png?t=1739957635\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/new_skill_tree.png?t=1739957635\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hop on your hoverboard, grab the ball with your chain, and use its swinging power to perform diverse actions.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dunk, shoot, block, and steal the ball while using the nitro to boost your speed or perform double or triple jumps!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Use your Perk Points in different Perk Trees to customize your play style!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/vs_best_riders_600x104_.png?t=1739957635\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/Add_a_heading__3_.png?t=1739957635\" /><strong>Compete against other riders in various PvP game modes, including 2v2 and 3v3 Quick Matches, or hone your skills in Academy, Champion Road, Free Play, or Custom Match modes!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/best_on_court_600x104_.png?t=1739957635\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/Add_a_heading__4_.png?t=1739957635\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>After each match, you will receive MVP points depending on the result. So make sure to win and to be the best Rider to receive a bonus!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The more you have MVP points, the more you will unlock rewards!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/custom_with_style_600x104_.png?t=1739957635\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/Add_a_heading__6_.png?t=1739957635\" /><strong>With your hard-earned Metanium and MVP points, progress in the Metapass, and try to collect your favorite equipment and items to use in the game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Items shown may require separate purchases from the in-game store and are subject to availability. Contains in-game purchases.</i></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to Metaball","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2215910/d9e00d8b8d1ffab3c45cc39b3b1dda0802827516.jpg"},{"name":"Practice is the key","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2215910/d9e00d8b8d1ffab3c45cc39b3b1dda0802827516.jpg"},{"name":"First Goal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2215910/d9e00d8b8d1ffab3c45cc39b3b1dda0802827516.jpg"},{"name":"Metaball Mania","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2215910/84a0264647f113a5e08116ada116b